info.name: Stylish Extension - Dark Theme
info.description: Darkens the entire Stylish Extension and the Stylish Extension popup when you click on the extension in the bar to the right of the omnibox.
info.additionalInfo:
Supported Browsers:
* Chrome
* Edge
* Opera
* Brave
+ all other Chromium based browsers

Unsupported Browsers:
* Firefox: doesn't allow theming extension pages
* Safari: Stylish isn't even made for this browser
+ all other Gecko based browsers
